# Color & Theme Rules

Full palette and semantic rules are documented in `/THEME.md`. Always read it before adding or changing any color.

**Quick reference:**

- CTAs on **dark bg** → `#D4C4A8` sand fill, `#1A1814` text
- CTAs on **light bg** → `#4DCCE8` cyan fill, `#07080C` text
- Accent / focus rings / progress bars → `#4DCCE8` cyan only
- Selected states on light bg → `#1A1814` fill, `#EDE6D8` text
- **Banned**: `#2F34F4` electric blue — do not use anywhere

**Hero is frozen** — never propose color changes to `components/sections/Hero.tsx` unless the user explicitly asks.
